69
00:03:29.167 --> 00:03:30.251 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Precisely.</c.bg_transparent>

70
00:03:30.585 --> 00:03:31.461 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>In here.</c.bg_transparent>

71
00:03:51.064 --> 00:03:54.150 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
