<c.bg_transparent>"Welcome."</c.bg_transparent>

80
00:04:18.633 --> 00:04:20.969 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Here's where it gets interesting.</c.bg_transparent>

81
00:04:28.393 --> 00:04:30.311 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see you recognize it.</c.bg_transparent>

82
00:04:31.896 --> 00:04:33.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Wha-what? I don't.</c.bg_transparent>

83
00:04:34.148 --> 00:04:35.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It says...</c.bg_transparent>

84
00:04:36.234 --> 00:04:37.986 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Welcome, Emissary."</c.bg_transparent>

85
00:04:39.153 --> 00:04:41.948 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now you know why I asked you here.</c.bg_transparent>

86
00:04:50.498 --> 00:04:52.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Sisko has come.</c.bg_transparent>

87
00:04:52.750 --> 00:04:54.460 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The circle is complete.</c.bg_transparent>

88
00:04:55.753 --> 00:04:57.755 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Reckoning must begin.</c.bg_transparent>

89
00:04:58.339 --> 00:04:59.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Reckoning?</c.bg_transparent>

90
00:04:59.757 --> 00:05:01.634 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Much will depend on the Sisko.</c.bg_transparent>

91
00:05:03.594 --> 00:05:05.221 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He is corporeal.</c.bg_transparent>

92
00:05:06.764 --> 00:05:07.849 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Limited.</c.bg_transparent>

93
00:05:08.891 --> 00:05:10.268 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He is the Sisko.</c.bg_transparent>

94
00:05:10.643 --> 00:05:11.978 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He will not waver.</c.bg_transparent>

95
00:05:13.354 --> 00:05:14.522 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He is of Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

96
00:05:15.606 --> 00:05:17.108 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He will bring the Reckoning.</c.bg_transparent>

97
