<c.bg_transparent>What is it you expect of me?</c.bg_transparent>

98
00:05:19.819 --> 00:05:21.654 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It will be the end.</c.bg_transparent>

99
00:05:22.822 --> 00:05:24.115 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Or the beginning.</c.bg_transparent>

100
00:05:24.866 --> 00:05:26.159 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't understand.</c.bg_transparent>

101
00:05:26.534 --> 00:05:28.077 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Sisko will know.</c.bg_transparent>

102
00:05:32.332 --> 00:05:33.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

103
00:07:45.047 --> 00:07:46.090 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dad?</c.bg_transparent>

104
00:07:46.632 --> 00:07:47.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you okay?</c.bg_transparent>

105
00:07:48.092 --> 00:07:49.093 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

106
00:07:49.427 --> 00:07:50.386 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeah.</c.bg_transparent>

107
00:07:53.681 --> 00:07:54.974 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets...</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:07:55.516 --> 00:07:56.767 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>they were here.</c.bg_transparent>

109
00:07:57.477 --> 00:07:58.811 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>They spoke to me.</c.bg_transparent>

110
00:07:58.895 --> 00:08:01.564 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>You had a vision, Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We saw nothing.</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:08:01.647 --> 00:08:02.607 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>What did they say?</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:08:02.690 --> 00:08:04.942 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>They mentioned something</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about a Reckoning.</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:08:05.026 --> 00:08:06.611 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that a part of some prophecy?</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:08:06.694 --> 00:08:07.987 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not one that I know of.</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:08:08.321 --> 00:08:09.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's get out of here.</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:08:10.198 --> 00:08:12.450 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's all right, Jake.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We'll be leaving soon.</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:08:12.575 --> 00:08:16.662 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have got to find out</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what those inscriptions say.</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:08:17.663 --> 00:08:19.749 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish we could translate them</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>more quickly</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:08:19.832 --> 00:08:21.959 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>but we don't have the resources.</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:08:22.043 --> 00:08:24.003 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fortunately, we do.</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:08:28.633 --> 00:08:32.345 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had a pretty good idea what this was</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the minute I laid eyes on it.</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:08:33.638 --> 00:08:34.972 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>That confirms it.</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:08:35.348 --> 00:08:37.934 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a slab of stone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with some writing on it.</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:08:38.017 --> 00:08:39.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dax...</c.bg_transparent>

125
00:08:39.393 --> 00:08:41.687 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you want me to say, Benjamin?</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:08:42.188 --> 00:08:44.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not picking up any</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>residual energy readings--</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:08:44.941 --> 00:08:48.361 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>certainly nothing that would explain</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>how it threw you across the room.</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:08:48.444 --> 00:08:50.696 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want you to translate the inscriptions.</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:08:51.822 --> 00:08:53.783 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was afraid you were going to say that.</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:08:56.118 --> 00:08:58.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Ranjen's translation program.</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:08:58.454 --> 00:09:00.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not complete,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but at least it's a start.</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:09:01.916 --> 00:09:03.084 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good luck.</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:09:09.173 --> 00:09:10.341 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:09:11.259 --> 00:09:12.510 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chimes jingling )</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:09:12.593 --> 00:09:14.470 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>CLERGYMAN: Services are about to begin.</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:09:21.769 --> 00:09:24.105 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Captain, services are about to begin.</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:09:28.734 --> 00:09:30.152 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>WORF: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Ops to Captain Sisko.</i></c.bg_transparent>

138
00:09:30.236 --> 00:09:31.404 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:09:31.487 --> 00:09:33.656 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>WORF: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>We just received</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>a communication from Bajor.</i></c.bg_transparent>

140
00:09:33.739 --> 00:09:35.783 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kai Winn is on her way to the station.</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:09:52.258 --> 00:09:54.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Welcome to Deep Space Nine, Your Eminence.</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:09:55.011 --> 00:09:56.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you, Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:09:56.512 --> 00:09:58.139 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What brings you to the station?</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:09:58.222 --> 00:10:00.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I should think that would be clear.</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:10:00.766 --> 00:10:03.936 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You removed an artifact</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from an archaeological site</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:10:04.020 --> 00:10:05.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>without consulting the Vedek Assembly.</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:10:06.981 --> 00:10:08.566 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I meant no disrespect.</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:10:08.649 --> 00:10:12.612 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can understand</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>how we would be sensitive to such matters.</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:10:13.362 --> 00:10:14.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>During the Occupation,</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:10:14.697 --> 00:10:17.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>the Cardassians plundered</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Bajor's historical treasures</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:10:17.742 --> 00:10:19.327 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>as if it were their right.</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:10:19.994 --> 00:10:23.664 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I never imagined that you would behave</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in such a manner.</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:10:23.748 --> 00:10:26.292 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I assure you that the artifact</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>will be returned</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:10:26.375 --> 00:10:28.294 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>as soon as I've finished studying it.</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:10:28.377 --> 00:10:31.881 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was not aware that you had</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>expertise in Bajoran history.</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:10:31.964 --> 00:10:34.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I don't.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Then why not leave the artifact</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:10:35.009 --> 00:10:36.886 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>in the hands of those who do?</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:10:37.136 --> 00:10:38.846 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are scholars on Bajor</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:10:38.929 --> 00:10:41.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>who've devoted their lives</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the study of such things.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:10:42.224 --> 00:10:44.894 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand, but I brought it here</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:10:44.977 --> 00:10:47.396 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>because I believe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that's what the Prophets want.</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:10:47.521 --> 00:10:48.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see.</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:10:48.731 --> 00:10:52.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then I take it this has something to do</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with your vision?</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:10:52.693 --> 00:10:53.736 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Exactly.</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:10:55.237 --> 00:10:56.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Forgive me.</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:10:56.364 --> 00:10:59.367 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I-I didn't realize</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that the Prophets told you</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:10:59.450 --> 00:11:01.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to bring the relic here.</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:11:01.285 --> 00:11:03.913 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, they didn't... not in so many words.</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:11:04.330 --> 00:11:05.581 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see.</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:11:06.248 --> 00:11:08.376 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then exactly what did they say?</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:11:09.251 --> 00:11:10.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:11:10.878 --> 00:11:12.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's difficult to explain.</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:11:13.714 --> 00:11:15.424 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets are not always clear.</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:11:16.217 --> 00:11:18.886 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, since they have never spoken to me</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:11:19.553 --> 00:11:21.639 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll have to take your word for it.</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:11:22.348 --> 00:11:25.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All I know is, for now, it belongs here.</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:11:27.311 --> 00:11:30.731 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who am I to argue</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with the Emissary of the Prophets?</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:11:38.030 --> 00:11:42.493 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And then she contacted Starfleet</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and lodged a formal protest.</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:11:43.119 --> 00:11:45.413 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that why Admiral Ross</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>wanted to talk to you?</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:11:46.372 --> 00:11:47.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, how'd it go?</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:11:47.957 --> 00:11:50.626 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He told me to stop meddling</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in Bajoran affairs</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:11:50.709 --> 00:11:52.503 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and return the damn tablet.</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:11:52.795 --> 00:11:55.798 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know how Starfleet feels</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about this Emissary thing.</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:11:56.173 --> 00:11:59.051 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It makes them very uncomfortable</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that you've allowed the Bajorans</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:11:59.135 --> 00:12:01.470 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to view you as a religious icon.</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:12:02.555 --> 00:12:04.598 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It used to make you uncomfortable, too.</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:12:05.099 --> 00:12:06.434 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not anymore.</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:12:07.143 --> 00:12:10.813 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess the Prophets have spoken to me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>one too many times.</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:12:10.896 --> 00:12:14.108 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I remember when you used</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to call them "wormhole aliens."</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:12:14.233 --> 00:12:17.903 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Wormhole aliens or Prophets...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it really doesn't matter.</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:12:18.112 --> 00:12:22.074 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The fact is, they exist out of time</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and over the centuries</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:12:22.158 --> 00:12:25.035 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>they've given the Bajorans</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>glimpses of the future</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:12:25.119 --> 00:12:27.037 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>glimpses that the Bajorans</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have written down</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:12:27.121 --> 00:12:28.998 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to help them guide succeeding generations.</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:12:29.081 --> 00:12:34.044 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If whatever is written here</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>can help me avoid mistakes</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:12:34.128 --> 00:12:37.381 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>can help me make the right decisions</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>then I'd be a fool to ignore it.</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:12:37.923 --> 00:12:40.551 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fair enough, but if you don't mind</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:12:40.634 --> 00:12:43.637 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to continue to think</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of them as wormhole aliens.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:12:44.263 --> 00:12:45.723 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All I know is...</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:12:46.515 --> 00:12:49.727 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>that they have a relationship with Bajor</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:12:50.311 --> 00:12:52.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>that stretches back over a thousand years.</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:12:52.563 --> 00:12:55.191 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They care what happens to Bajorans.</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:12:55.316 --> 00:12:57.568 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They proved that</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when they kept the Dominion fleet</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:12:57.651 --> 00:12:58.944 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>from coming through the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:12:59.028 --> 00:13:00.821 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Didn't you have to talk them into it?</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:13:01.739 --> 00:13:05.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Didn't they say they would exact</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>some kind of penance for helping you?</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:13:05.743 --> 00:13:07.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, but they listened,</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:13:08.787 --> 00:13:11.874 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and they saved Bajor</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and the rest of the Alpha Quadrant.</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:13:11.957 --> 00:13:14.502 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now they're asking me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for something in return.</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:13:14.585 --> 00:13:16.420 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know what it is yet</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:13:16.629 --> 00:13:19.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I'm not going to return</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the tablet until I do.</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:13:19.632 --> 00:13:22.301 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's the key. I can feel it.</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:13:22.384 --> 00:13:24.345 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hope you're wrong about that, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:13:24.720 --> 00:13:25.888 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What have you got?</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:13:25.971 --> 00:13:28.432 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The computer has translated</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>part of the inscription.</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:13:28.516 --> 00:13:30.976 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It probably lacks the eloquence</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the original passage</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:13:31.060 --> 00:13:32.853 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but you'll get the gist of it.</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:13:33.896 --> 00:13:35.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Here it is in modern Bajoran.</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:13:37.983 --> 00:13:40.736 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: "The time of Reckoning is at hand.</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:13:41.570 --> 00:13:43.113 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>"The Prophets will weep.</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:13:44.240 --> 00:13:46.116 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Their sorrow will consume...</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:13:50.579 --> 00:13:53.499 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>the Gateway to the Temple."</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:13:55.042 --> 00:13:56.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell me I'm wrong...</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:13:58.462 --> 00:14:01.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but isn't the Gateway</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the Temple Deep Space Nine?</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:14:11.767 --> 00:14:13.894 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was just telling you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what the translation said.</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:14:13.978 --> 00:14:15.437 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I did not say I believed it.</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:14:15.521 --> 00:14:16.855 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I'm not worried.</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:14:16.939 --> 00:14:19.108 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you look hard enough</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you'll find a Bajoran prophecy</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:14:19.191 --> 00:14:20.109 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for just about anything.</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:14:20.192 --> 00:14:23.070 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The ancient texts are a tangle</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of vague contradictions.</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:14:23.153 --> 00:14:25.072 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, this one is anything but vague</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:14:25.155 --> 00:14:27.825 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and Bajoran prophecies</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have an odd way of coming true.</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:14:27.908 --> 00:14:29.535 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't say you believe in this stuff, too?</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:14:29.618 --> 00:14:31.704 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo believes in preparing for the worst.</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:14:31.787 --> 00:14:32.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>True.</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:14:32.913 --> 00:14:34.874 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's as bad as the Bajorans.</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:14:35.958 --> 00:14:38.878 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Business hasn't been this slow</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>since the Dominion was here.</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:14:40.296 --> 00:14:42.673 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know, I feel I have a civic duty</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:14:42.756 --> 00:14:44.884 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to do something</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about all this doom and gloom</c.bg_transparent>

240
00:14:44.967 --> 00:14:47.428 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>which is why I want to tell you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that I've extended happy hour.</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:14:47.511 --> 00:14:48.804 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Extended it?</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:14:49.680 --> 00:14:52.349 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>From now on, every hour is happy hour...</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:14:53.142 --> 00:14:54.852 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>at least until business picks up.</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:14:54.935 --> 00:14:56.395 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eat, drink, and be merry.</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:14:56.478 --> 00:14:58.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For tomorrow, we die.</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:14:59.565 --> 00:15:02.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So what does the Captain say about this?</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:15:02.568 --> 00:15:04.028 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He is reserving judgment</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:15:04.111 --> 00:15:05.988 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>until the computer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>has finished the translation.</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:15:06.196 --> 00:15:08.657 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who knows? The rest</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the tablet probably says</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:15:08.741 --> 00:15:10.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Go to Quark's. It's happy hour."</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:15:10.701 --> 00:15:12.077 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I like the way you think, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:15:12.161 --> 00:15:14.914 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, this is ridiculous.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Nothing's going to happen.</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:15:15.039 --> 00:15:16.874 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Someday, we're all going</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to look back on this and laugh.</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:15:18.083 --> 00:15:20.294 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( deep rumbling )</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:15:20.961 --> 00:15:22.212 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO: What was that?</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:15:34.850 --> 00:15:36.685 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( deep rumbling )</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:15:39.438 --> 00:15:41.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How did that prophecy go again?</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:15:46.820 --> 00:15:48.697 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KIRA: You don't have to do this, you know.</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:15:48.781 --> 00:15:50.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO: Don't have to do what?</c.bg_transparent>

260
00:15:50.908 --> 00:15:53.369 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sit here, watch me eat.</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:15:54.036 --> 00:15:56.705 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't mind.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>In fact, I rather enjoy it.</c.bg_transparent>

262
00:15:57.456 --> 00:15:59.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You eat with such gusto...</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:16:00.751 --> 00:16:01.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>most of the time.</c.bg_transparent>

264
00:16:02.544 --> 00:16:03.921 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not today.</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:16:06.882 --> 00:16:09.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just wish that we knew more</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about the Reckoning.</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:16:09.426 --> 00:16:12.179 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It would give us a better idea</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of what the Prophets want from us.</c.bg_transparent>

267
00:16:13.722 --> 00:16:17.184 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It seems to me that, if the Prophets</c.bg_transparent>

268
00:16:17.267 --> 00:16:19.645 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>want the Bajoran people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to follow a given path</c.bg_transparent>

269
00:16:19.728 --> 00:16:22.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>they should provide</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>more specific directions.</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:16:23.774 --> 00:16:25.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It doesn't work like that.</c.bg_transparent>

271
00:16:25.275 --> 00:16:26.860 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe it should.</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:16:27.194 --> 00:16:29.488 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Kai would say that you lack faith.</c.bg_transparent>

273
00:16:30.990 --> 00:16:32.533 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you would agree.</c.bg_transparent>

274
00:16:33.784 --> 00:16:36.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just don't know how people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>make it through the day without it.</c.bg_transparent>

275
00:16:38.080 --> 00:16:39.415 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We manage.</c.bg_transparent>

276
00:16:40.541 --> 00:16:42.876 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Besides, I do have faith in some things.</c.bg_transparent>

277
00:16:43.127 --> 00:16:44.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckling ) Such as?</c.bg_transparent>

278
00:16:44.920 --> 00:16:45.838 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You.</c.bg_transparent>

279
00:16:49.758 --> 00:16:51.552 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll try not to disappoint you.</c.bg_transparent>

280
00:16:55.931 --> 00:16:58.684 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No doubt you've heard</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the latest news from Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

281
00:16:59.184 --> 00:17:01.979 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>About the flooding</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the Rakantha Province, yes.</c.bg_transparent>

282
00:17:03.480 --> 00:17:07.568 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There was also an earthquake</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the Kendra Valley last night.</c.bg_transparent>

283
00:17:08.068 --> 00:17:11.113 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This morning, a tornado struck Tamulna.</c.bg_transparent>

284
00:17:11.613 --> 00:17:14.241 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Our sensors indicate</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that Bajor has been affected</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:17:14.324 --> 00:17:15.993 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>by the instability of the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:17:16.076 --> 00:17:17.494 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How comforting.</c.bg_transparent>

287
00:17:17.745 --> 00:17:20.581 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell me, do your sensors</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have an explanation</c.bg_transparent>

288
00:17:20.664 --> 00:17:22.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for the instability itself?</c.bg_transparent>

289
00:17:24.001 --> 00:17:25.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

290
00:17:25.544 --> 00:17:27.129 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then I'll give you one.</c.bg_transparent>

291
00:17:28.505 --> 00:17:32.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've angered the Prophets</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by taking the tablet from Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

292
00:17:32.551 --> 00:17:35.012 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>As the spiritual leader</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the Bajoran people</c.bg_transparent>

293
00:17:35.095 --> 00:17:37.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm asking you to return it.</c.bg_transparent>

294
00:17:37.890 --> 00:17:39.767 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And as the Emissary of the Prophets</c.bg_transparent>

295
00:17:39.850 --> 00:17:42.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I will ask you to give me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>more time to study it.</c.bg_transparent>

296
00:17:42.603 --> 00:17:44.563 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I believe it is the will of the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

297
00:17:45.105 --> 00:17:46.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I disagree.</c.bg_transparent>

298
00:17:46.940 --> 00:17:49.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is a formal request</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from the First Minister</c.bg_transparent>

299
00:17:49.610 --> 00:17:52.237 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for you to turn over the relic to me.</c.bg_transparent>

300
00:17:52.738 --> 00:17:55.407 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You must have been very persuasive.</c.bg_transparent>

301
00:17:55.574 --> 00:17:58.911 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is the first time</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you and Shakaar have agreed on anything.</c.bg_transparent>

302
00:18:00.120 --> 00:18:03.207 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you deny his request, I promise you</c.bg_transparent>

303
00:18:03.290 --> 00:18:07.586 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>it will damage relations</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>between Bajor and the Federation.</c.bg_transparent>

304
00:18:14.343 --> 00:18:15.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The tablet...</c.bg_transparent>

305
00:18:17.012 --> 00:18:19.723 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>will be on its way to Bajor</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on the morning transport.</c.bg_transparent>

306
00:18:19.807 --> 00:18:20.933 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( places padd on desk )</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:18:25.646 --> 00:18:26.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>As will I.</c.bg_transparent>

308
00:18:34.530 --> 00:18:37.783 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're sending it back?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>And I was just starting to have fun.</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:18:37.866 --> 00:18:41.662 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not letting you off the hook, old man.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I need these inscriptions translated.</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:18:42.246 --> 00:18:45.290 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can work off the holo-recordings</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I took yesterday.</c.bg_transparent>

311
00:18:45.374 --> 00:18:47.042 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Have you made any more progress?</c.bg_transparent>

312
00:18:48.293 --> 00:18:49.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good news or bad?</c.bg_transparent>

313
00:18:49.461 --> 00:18:50.754 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-That depends.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-On what?</c.bg_transparent>

314
00:18:50.838 --> 00:18:52.589 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>On what this ideogram means.</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:18:52.673 --> 00:18:54.591 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The computer has given me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>two possibilities.</c.bg_transparent>

316
00:18:54.675 --> 00:18:55.592 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They are?</c.bg_transparent>

317
00:18:56.343 --> 00:18:57.761 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>During the Reckoning</c.bg_transparent>

318
00:18:57.845 --> 00:18:59.972 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>the Bajorans will either "suffer horribly"</c.bg_transparent>

319
00:19:00.055 --> 00:19:02.015 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>or "eat fruit."</c.bg_transparent>

320
00:19:03.809 --> 00:19:04.810 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Eat fruit"?</c.bg_transparent>

321
00:19:06.728 --> 00:19:09.439 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Given the tone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the rest of the inscriptions</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:19:10.899 --> 00:19:12.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I would bet on horrible suffering.</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:19:13.193 --> 00:19:14.403 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What else do you have?</c.bg_transparent>

324
00:19:14.820 --> 00:19:17.531 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll love this. It's about you.</c.bg_transparent>

325
00:19:18.699 --> 00:19:22.411 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Once the Reckoning begins,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Emissary will..."</c.bg_transparent>

326
00:19:23.203 --> 00:19:24.246 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go on.</c.bg_transparent>

327
00:19:24.329 --> 00:19:25.873 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was hoping you could tell me.</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:19:26.582 --> 00:19:28.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, the rest of the</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>inscription's damaged.</c.bg_transparent>

329
00:19:28.917 --> 00:19:30.419 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, that figures.</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:19:30.502 --> 00:19:32.671 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( deep rumbling )</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:19:32.754 --> 00:19:34.923 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I wish the wormhole</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>would stop doing that.</c.bg_transparent>

332
00:19:35.007 --> 00:19:36.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So do I. Keep at it, old man.</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:19:37.009 --> 00:19:38.510 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just do me one favor.</c.bg_transparent>

334
00:19:38.594 --> 00:19:42.181 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you talk to the Prophets again</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>ask for a dictionary...</c.bg_transparent>

335
00:19:43.015 --> 00:19:44.057 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>please.</c.bg_transparent>

336
00:19:44.433 --> 00:19:46.101 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll see what I can do.</c.bg_transparent>

337
00:19:46.185 --> 00:19:47.144 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you.</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:19:53.942 --> 00:19:56.987 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Captain, I have a message for you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from General Martok.</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:19:57.070 --> 00:19:58.030 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

340
00:19:58.113 --> 00:20:00.282 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's dispatched</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>three Klingon attack cruisers</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:20:00.365 --> 00:20:03.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to bolster the defense perimeter</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>around the Dorala system.</c.bg_transparent>

342
00:20:03.285 --> 00:20:07.581 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good. I just hope they can hold out</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>until Starfleet sends in reinforcements.</c.bg_transparent>

343
00:20:07.664 --> 00:20:10.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Klingons will hold out.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Martok will see to it.</c.bg_transparent>

344
00:20:14.296 --> 00:20:15.672 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Long day?</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:20:16.048 --> 00:20:17.507 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They seem to get longer.</c.bg_transparent>

346
00:20:18.383 --> 00:20:20.177 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll feel better in the morning...</c.bg_transparent>

347
00:20:20.886 --> 00:20:22.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>once the Kai is off the station.</c.bg_transparent>

348
00:20:22.512 --> 00:20:24.473 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckling )</c.bg_transparent>

349
00:20:24.556 --> 00:20:27.392 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She may be the spiritual leader</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of millions of Bajorans</c.bg_transparent>

350
00:20:27.476 --> 00:20:29.811 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but she is not an easy woman to like.</c.bg_transparent>

351
00:20:29.895 --> 00:20:32.981 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, if it's any comfort</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I don't think she likes you, either.</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:20:33.065 --> 00:20:34.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've known that for a while.</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:20:34.858 --> 00:20:36.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess I should have consulted her</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:20:36.443 --> 00:20:38.820 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>before I brought the artifact</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>up to the station.</c.bg_transparent>

355
00:20:38.904 --> 00:20:40.656 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She would have tried to stop you.</c.bg_transparent>

356
00:20:40.739 --> 00:20:42.991 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah... that's why I didn't ask her.</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:20:43.492 --> 00:20:45.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>In a way, I feel sorry for her.</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:20:45.327 --> 00:20:48.747 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She spends her whole life</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in service to the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

359
00:20:48.830 --> 00:20:52.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then one day, after years</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of self-sacrifice and commitment</c.bg_transparent>

360
00:20:53.043 --> 00:20:55.504 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>she gets her reward. She's elected Kai.</c.bg_transparent>

361
00:20:55.837 --> 00:20:58.048 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Should've been the greatest</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>moment of her life.</c.bg_transparent>

362
00:21:00.550 --> 00:21:03.595 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But my being the Emissary</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>spoiled it for her.</c.bg_transparent>

363
00:21:03.845 --> 00:21:06.890 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, the Kai's always been</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the spiritual leader of Bajor</c.bg_transparent>

364
00:21:06.974 --> 00:21:09.268 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but Winn has to share that role with you</c.bg_transparent>

365
00:21:09.351 --> 00:21:10.686 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and to make matters worse</c.bg_transparent>

366
00:21:11.019 --> 00:21:12.771 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>you're an outsider, a non-Bajoran.</c.bg_transparent>

367
00:21:12.854 --> 00:21:14.940 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's something</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>she can never forgive you for.</c.bg_transparent>

368
00:21:15.023 --> 00:21:18.068 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess that's why she made</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>such an issue of the whole thing.</c.bg_transparent>

369
00:21:18.360 --> 00:21:20.070 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, she's jealous of you</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:21:20.153 --> 00:21:23.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and of your relationship</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:21:24.157 --> 00:21:25.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm a little envious myself.</c.bg_transparent>

372
00:21:25.826 --> 00:21:27.452 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why?</c.bg_transparent>

373
00:21:27.911 --> 00:21:30.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You speak with the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

374
00:21:30.372 --> 00:21:31.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They listen to you.</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:21:31.832 --> 00:21:33.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's...</c.bg_transparent>

376
00:21:33.166 --> 00:21:35.002 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>that's a rare gift.</c.bg_transparent>

377
00:21:35.419 --> 00:21:37.337 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Certainly nothing I asked for.</c.bg_transparent>

378
00:21:37.421 --> 00:21:41.508 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess that's why I don't</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>resent you, but the Kai does.</c.bg_transparent>

379
00:21:44.177 --> 00:21:45.887 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll keep that in mind.</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:21:59.526 --> 00:22:01.069 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is something wrong, Eminence?</c.bg_transparent>

381
00:22:02.863 --> 00:22:04.573 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What makes you say that, child?</c.bg_transparent>

382
00:22:04.656 --> 00:22:05.782 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You seem troubled.</c.bg_transparent>

383
00:22:05.866 --> 00:22:07.117 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not at all.</c.bg_transparent>

384
00:22:07.492 --> 00:22:08.869 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am quite relieved</c.bg_transparent>

385
00:22:08.952 --> 00:22:11.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>the Emissary has decided</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to do the right thing.</c.bg_transparent>

386
00:22:11.997 --> 00:22:13.749 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, you didn't leave him</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>much choice, did you?</c.bg_transparent>

387
00:22:14.916 --> 00:22:18.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I suppose you think</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I enjoyed forcing his hand.</c.bg_transparent>

388
00:22:19.463 --> 00:22:21.965 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I assure you, I did not.</c.bg_transparent>

389
00:22:22.341 --> 00:22:26.303 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish the situation had been resolved</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>more amicably.</c.bg_transparent>

390
00:22:26.470 --> 00:22:28.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps the next time</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we have a disagreement</c.bg_transparent>

391
00:22:28.930 --> 00:22:31.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>he'll consider my wishes</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>more thoughtfully.</c.bg_transparent>

392
00:22:31.349 --> 00:22:32.392 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The next time?</c.bg_transparent>

393
00:22:32.476 --> 00:22:34.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're anticipating more disagreements?</c.bg_transparent>

394
00:22:36.188 --> 00:22:39.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I merely meant to express</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>my hope that, in the future</c.bg_transparent>

395
00:22:39.316 --> 00:22:41.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>we can work together</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for the good of Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

396
00:22:41.902 --> 00:22:42.903 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course.</c.bg_transparent>

397
00:22:42.986 --> 00:22:45.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>After all, you are on the same side,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>aren't you?</c.bg_transparent>

398
00:22:45.906 --> 00:22:47.157 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Naturally.</c.bg_transparent>

399
00:22:47.824 --> 00:22:49.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We both serve the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

400
00:22:49.951 --> 00:22:51.912 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There is no higher calling.</c.bg_transparent>

401
00:22:55.791 --> 00:22:58.585 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( deep rumbling )</c.bg_transparent>

402
00:23:01.004 --> 00:23:02.589 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

403
00:23:02.672 --> 00:23:03.590 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door chimes )</c.bg_transparent>

404
00:23:03.673 --> 00:23:04.591 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes?</c.bg_transparent>

405
00:23:06.218 --> 00:23:07.135 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Jake-o.</c.bg_transparent>

406
00:23:14.601 --> 00:23:16.061 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're up late.</c.bg_transparent>

407
00:23:16.353 --> 00:23:17.979 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, so are you.</c.bg_transparent>

408
00:23:18.063 --> 00:23:19.189 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's on your mind?</c.bg_transparent>

409
00:23:20.524 --> 00:23:22.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know. I guess I just wanted to see</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if you're all right.</c.bg_transparent>

410
00:23:24.694 --> 00:23:25.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm fine.</c.bg_transparent>

411
00:23:26.113 --> 00:23:28.573 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Since when did you become a worrier?</c.bg_transparent>

412
00:23:30.325 --> 00:23:31.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know.</c.bg_transparent>

413
00:23:32.536 --> 00:23:34.412 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's this Emissary stuff.</c.bg_transparent>

414
00:23:35.038 --> 00:23:36.456 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It scares me a little.</c.bg_transparent>

415
00:23:43.839 --> 00:23:45.132 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Twice now...</c.bg_transparent>

416
00:23:45.382 --> 00:23:47.008 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>twice in one year...</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:23:48.093 --> 00:23:50.387 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dr. Bashir's called me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>down to the Infirmary</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:23:50.470 --> 00:23:52.430 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to tell me something was wrong with you</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:23:53.056 --> 00:23:54.474 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and there you were</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:23:55.433 --> 00:23:58.603 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>lying unconscious on a bio-bed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>having visions or something.</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:24:00.730 --> 00:24:01.815 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And there...</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:24:01.898 --> 00:24:04.025 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>all I could do was just stand there</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:24:05.235 --> 00:24:06.611 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and, and wonder...</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:24:07.612 --> 00:24:09.322 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>if you were ever going to wake up.</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:24:12.367 --> 00:24:14.661 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know it hasn't been easy, Jake.</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:24:15.495 --> 00:24:17.205 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want it to happen again.</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:24:21.293 --> 00:24:25.088 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know, I didn't ask</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be the Emissary...</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:24:27.174 --> 00:24:31.219 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but, for better or worse,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I guess that's what I am...</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:24:34.139 --> 00:24:35.682 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>except for being your dad.</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:25:21.311 --> 00:25:26.524 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why do you always have to be</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>so damned mysterious?</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:25:28.443 --> 00:25:30.111 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Answer me.</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:25:31.613 --> 00:25:33.865 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am tired of your riddles!</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:25:35.325 --> 00:25:39.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If there's something</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you need me to do, say so!</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:25:43.333 --> 00:25:44.501 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( yelling )</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:26:12.779 --> 00:26:14.239 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let me guess.</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:26:14.739 --> 00:26:17.117 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You accidentally knocked it over.</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:26:17.951 --> 00:26:19.077 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not exactly.</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:26:19.160 --> 00:26:20.370 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't think so.</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:26:20.453 --> 00:26:22.747 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So what did happen?</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:26:23.832 --> 00:26:27.043 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just had this uncontrollable urge</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:26:27.127 --> 00:26:28.878 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to smash the tablet.</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:26:29.296 --> 00:26:31.298 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I get those urges all the time.</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:26:31.756 --> 00:26:33.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course, I never act on them.</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:26:35.969 --> 00:26:39.222 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not reading</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>any residual energy signatures.</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:26:39.306 --> 00:26:42.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's impossible.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Check the station's internal sensors.</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:26:44.811 --> 00:26:45.979 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nothing.</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:26:46.062 --> 00:26:47.772 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I tell you, I saw something.</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:26:47.856 --> 00:26:49.149 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We believe you, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:26:49.232 --> 00:26:51.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, please, Constable, don't patronize me.</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:26:56.031 --> 00:26:57.532 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sisko to Ops. Report.</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:26:57.615 --> 00:27:00.118 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We just experienced</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a station-wide power drain.</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:27:00.201 --> 00:27:01.828 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're attempting to determine the source.</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:27:02.078 --> 00:27:03.038 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Keep me informed.</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:27:03.121 --> 00:27:04.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>WORF: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Aye, sir.</i></c.bg_transparent>

455
00:27:04.456 --> 00:27:10.086 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's possible the power drain is related</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to this energy discharge you saw.</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:27:11.046 --> 00:27:13.340 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm starting to think the same thing.</c.bg_transparent>

457
00:27:15.133 --> 00:27:18.345 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Benjamin, you're not getting</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>another urge, are you?</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:27:19.137 --> 00:27:20.221 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:27:23.350 --> 00:27:25.185 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've done what I needed to do.</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:27:26.895 --> 00:27:29.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know this might sound strange</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:27:30.398 --> 00:27:33.318 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I think the Prophets</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>wanted me to shatter the tablet.</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:27:33.443 --> 00:27:35.653 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Try explaining that to Kai Winn.</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:27:36.529 --> 00:27:39.032 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't believe that you'd be so petty</c.bg_transparent>

464
00:27:39.115 --> 00:27:42.619 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>as to destroy the artifact</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>rather than turn it over to me.</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:27:42.702 --> 00:27:44.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's not why I did it.</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:27:45.163 --> 00:27:48.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You expect me to believe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that the Prophets wanted you</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:27:48.583 --> 00:27:52.545 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to destroy a priceless piece</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of Bajor's history?</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:27:52.629 --> 00:27:54.714 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's exactly what you have to believe.</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:27:55.507 --> 00:27:57.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And why would they do that?</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:27:57.509 --> 00:27:59.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish I had an answer for you.</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:27:59.928 --> 00:28:02.180 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I'm sure you'll</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>come up with something.</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:28:05.225 --> 00:28:08.561 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You and I haven't always</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>seen things eye to eye</c.bg_transparent>

473
00:28:08.645 --> 00:28:10.271 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but we have one thing in common--</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:28:10.355 --> 00:28:13.108 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>we both believe that the Prophets</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have a plan for Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:28:13.191 --> 00:28:16.361 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, sometimes,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's not easy to see the path</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:28:16.444 --> 00:28:17.987 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>they've laid out for us.</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:28:18.905 --> 00:28:23.159 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Right now, I don't know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what they want from me</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:28:23.243 --> 00:28:26.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I'm willing to take a leap of faith</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and trust that they're guiding me</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:28:26.246 --> 00:28:28.957 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I'm asking you to</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>take that leap with me.</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:28:29.040 --> 00:28:32.252 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's no need</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for a leap of faith, Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:28:32.335 --> 00:28:34.838 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets have made it quite clear.</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:28:35.338 --> 00:28:39.384 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Two-thirds of the Rakantha wheat harvest</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have been destroyed by floods.</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:28:39.467 --> 00:28:42.011 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Earthquakes have devastated</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Kendra Province</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:28:42.095 --> 00:28:43.972 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>leaving hundreds homeless.</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:28:44.764 --> 00:28:47.475 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bajorans are suffering because of you.</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:28:47.642 --> 00:28:51.020 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're paying the price</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for your act of sacrilege.</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:28:53.732 --> 00:28:55.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Odo to Captain Sisko.</i></c.bg_transparent>

488
00:28:55.859 --> 00:28:57.152 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:28:57.235 --> 00:28:59.612 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> You'd better come down</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>to the Promenade, sir.</i></c.bg_transparent>

490
00:28:59.696 --> 00:29:00.864 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is there a problem?</c.bg_transparent>

491
00:29:00.947 --> 00:29:02.824 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> I'll let you be the judge of that.</i></c.bg_transparent>

492
00:29:15.128 --> 00:29:18.006 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think we've found the source</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the power fluctuations.</c.bg_transparent>

493
00:29:18.590 --> 00:29:20.675 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When I tried to talk to her,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>she ignored me.</c.bg_transparent>

494
00:29:27.849 --> 00:29:29.684 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( wind whistling )</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:29:29.768 --> 00:29:31.519 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( glass exploding )</c.bg_transparent>

496
00:29:45.867 --> 00:29:48.870 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( voice reverberating) You...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are the Sisko.</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:29:50.705 --> 00:29:52.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Keep your hands off your weapons.</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:29:52.999 --> 00:29:54.042 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a Prophet.</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:29:55.919 --> 00:29:57.921 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why have you taken this woman's body?</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:29:58.922 --> 00:30:00.799 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This vessel is willing.</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:30:02.759 --> 00:30:04.010 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Reckoning...</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:30:05.386 --> 00:30:06.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>it is time.</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:30:14.229 --> 00:30:16.397 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: The Reckoning... what is it?</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:30:16.606 --> 00:30:17.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The end...</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:30:18.650 --> 00:30:19.984 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>or the beginning.</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:30:20.068 --> 00:30:21.402 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't understand.</c.bg_transparent>

507
00:30:24.155 --> 00:30:26.199 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I await Kosst Amojan.</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:30:26.282 --> 00:30:27.826 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Evil One.</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:30:28.743 --> 00:30:32.539 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A Pah-wraith</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>banished from the Celestial Temple.</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:30:33.373 --> 00:30:36.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're saying a Pah-wraith</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>will take corporeal form as well?</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:30:37.043 --> 00:30:38.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The battle will be joined.</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:30:39.003 --> 00:30:41.673 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This battle... is it to be fought here?</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:30:41.756 --> 00:30:43.883 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bajor will be reborn.</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:30:44.843 --> 00:30:47.053 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Shabren's Fifth Prophecy--</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:30:48.012 --> 00:30:49.305 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>the Rebirth.</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:30:49.389 --> 00:30:53.393 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If the Evil One is destroyed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it will bring a thousand years of peace--</c.bg_transparent>

517
00:30:54.227 --> 00:30:57.313 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>the Golden Age of Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

518
00:30:58.606 --> 00:31:00.275 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If it is destroyed?</c.bg_transparent>

519
00:31:02.652 --> 00:31:04.696 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who will prevail is not known.</c.bg_transparent>

520
00:31:04.779 --> 00:31:06.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you want from me?</c.bg_transparent>

521
00:31:06.948 --> 00:31:09.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Am I supposed to help you in some way?</c.bg_transparent>

522
00:31:09.284 --> 00:31:13.204 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Sisko has completed his task.</c.bg_transparent>

523
00:31:16.624 --> 00:31:18.501 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Forgive my blindness.</c.bg_transparent>

524
00:31:21.671 --> 00:31:23.506 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Prophet, hear me.</c.bg_transparent>

525
00:31:23.715 --> 00:31:25.550 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am the Kai of Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

526
00:31:25.967 --> 00:31:30.096 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I offer myself to you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as your humble servant.</c.bg_transparent>

527
00:31:30.638 --> 00:31:32.390 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I await their vessel.</c.bg_transparent>

528
00:31:33.558 --> 00:31:34.809 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Speak to me.</c.bg_transparent>

529
00:31:34.893 --> 00:31:37.061 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell me what I should do.</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:31:47.614 --> 00:31:49.032 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're evacuating.</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:31:50.325 --> 00:31:51.784 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can't be serious.</c.bg_transparent>

532
00:31:51.868 --> 00:31:54.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This battle could destroy the station.</c.bg_transparent>

533
00:31:54.203 --> 00:31:55.872 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then don't let it be fought here.</c.bg_transparent>

534
00:31:56.372 --> 00:31:57.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't have any choice.</c.bg_transparent>

535
00:31:57.999 --> 00:31:59.334 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, you do.</c.bg_transparent>

536
00:31:59.667 --> 00:32:02.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We can flood the Promenade</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with chroniton radiation.</c.bg_transparent>

537
00:32:02.545 --> 00:32:04.881 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you suggesting that we kill a Prophet?</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:32:05.048 --> 00:32:06.007 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I won't do that.</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:32:06.090 --> 00:32:07.717 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>BASHIR: You don't have to.</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:32:07.800 --> 00:32:10.470 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you ramp up the chroniton levels slowly</c.bg_transparent>

541
00:32:10.553 --> 00:32:12.138 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you'll give the wormhole alien</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a chance to leave</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:32:12.221 --> 00:32:14.057 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kira's body without getting hurt.</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:32:14.265 --> 00:32:16.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: We have everything rigged</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and ready to go.</c.bg_transparent>

544
00:32:16.601 --> 00:32:17.769 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just say the word.</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:32:22.398 --> 00:32:23.441 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

546
00:32:23.816 --> 00:32:24.734 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:32:26.402 --> 00:32:29.447 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Deep Space Nine is critical</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the defense of the Federation.</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:32:29.530 --> 00:32:31.074 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We cannot risk destroying it.</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:32:31.407 --> 00:32:34.410 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When the Dominion fleet</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was about to come through the wormhole</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:32:34.994 --> 00:32:36.746 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I asked the Prophets for their help.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:32:36.829 --> 00:32:38.081 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They gave it to me.</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:32:38.373 --> 00:32:40.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now they're asking for my help.</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:32:40.917 --> 00:32:43.294 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They need to fight this battle here, now.</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:32:43.378 --> 00:32:45.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not going to jeopardize my crew</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:32:46.965 --> 00:32:49.884 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I'm not going to stand</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the way of the Prophets, either.</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:32:49.968 --> 00:32:51.594 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if the Prophets lose?</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:32:51.678 --> 00:32:53.846 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you willing to sacrifice Kira?</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:32:53.930 --> 00:32:57.058 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophet said she was willing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be their instrument.</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:32:57.141 --> 00:32:58.434 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you believe that?</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:32:58.518 --> 00:32:59.477 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I do.</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:33:03.022 --> 00:33:06.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know how important</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>her faith is to her and...</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:33:06.275 --> 00:33:09.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have no doubt that</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>she would allow the Prophets</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:33:09.195 --> 00:33:11.489 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to use her as their instrument.</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:33:14.909 --> 00:33:18.413 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll notify Starfleet that</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we're abandoning the station.</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:33:19.664 --> 00:33:21.499 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Begin the evacuation immediately.</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:33:34.012 --> 00:33:36.180 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO: Hurry along, now. Hurry along.</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:33:36.973 --> 00:33:38.558 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Is this transport full?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-There's room.</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:33:38.641 --> 00:33:40.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to check the</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Promenade for stragglers.</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:33:41.144 --> 00:33:45.398 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo, you should've helped us</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>persuade the Captain to end this.</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:33:45.481 --> 00:33:47.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had to respect Kira's wishes.</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:33:47.859 --> 00:33:50.445 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If it were Dax, I am not sure</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I could've done the same.</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:33:50.528 --> 00:33:53.072 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, just be grateful</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you didn't have to make that choice.</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:33:54.615 --> 00:33:57.452 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>For your sake, I hope</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Prophets are victorious.</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:33:57.535 --> 00:34:00.538 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They will be</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if Kira has anything to do with it.</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:34:02.915 --> 00:34:03.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come on.</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:34:06.669 --> 00:34:07.795 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Report.</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:34:07.879 --> 00:34:10.089 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We expect to be down to a skeleton crew</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>within the hour.</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:34:10.339 --> 00:34:11.424 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Very well.</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:34:11.507 --> 00:34:12.884 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What did Starfleet have to say?</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:34:13.217 --> 00:34:14.635 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I managed to convince them</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:34:14.719 --> 00:34:16.846 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that we couldn't afford</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to defy the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:34:16.929 --> 00:34:18.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>WORF: They are the only thing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that's keeping the Dominion</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:34:18.639 --> 00:34:20.099 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>from coming through the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:34:20.433 --> 00:34:23.936 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The only problem is, there's no guarantee</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Prophets will win this battle.</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:34:24.020 --> 00:34:25.313 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Odo to Sisko.</i></c.bg_transparent>

586
00:34:25.396 --> 00:34:26.773 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead, Constable.</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:34:26.856 --> 00:34:28.274 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Captain, there's a group of Bajorans</i></c.bg_transparent>

588
00:34:28.357 --> 00:34:30.902 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>on the Promenade</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>who are refusing to leave.</i></c.bg_transparent>

589
00:34:32.945 --> 00:34:38.159 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>WINN:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Tera dak embah</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>ihsehelm ran embah...</i></c.bg_transparent>

590
00:34:38.493 --> 00:34:40.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ALL: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>de-ram ta-meen.</i></c.bg_transparent>

591
00:34:42.413 --> 00:34:44.457 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Tera dak ihsehelm</i></c.bg_transparent>

592
00:34:44.540 --> 00:34:46.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>ran embah...</i></c.bg_transparent>

593
00:34:46.626 --> 00:34:48.252 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ALL: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>de-ram ta-meen...</i></c.bg_transparent>

594
00:34:48.336 --> 00:34:50.296 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The last transports are standing by.</c.bg_transparent>

595
00:34:51.089 --> 00:34:54.634 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>WINN:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Tera dak ihsehelm</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>ran embah...</i></c.bg_transparent>

596
00:34:55.259 --> 00:34:56.260 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eminence.</c.bg_transparent>

597
00:34:56.344 --> 00:34:57.637 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>...ta-meen.</i></c.bg_transparent>

598
00:35:00.098 --> 00:35:01.015 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:35:01.265 --> 00:35:02.683 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>These people have to go.</c.bg_transparent>

600
00:35:04.060 --> 00:35:06.604 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're offering prayers</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for the Prophets' victory.</c.bg_transparent>

601
00:35:07.146 --> 00:35:09.649 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets will hear your prayers</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>wherever you are.</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:35:09.732 --> 00:35:11.359 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It isn't safe here.</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:35:12.693 --> 00:35:15.113 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then why are you still here, Emissary?</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:35:15.571 --> 00:35:18.116 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophet told you your task was done.</c.bg_transparent>

605
00:35:18.407 --> 00:35:20.201 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am Captain of this station</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:35:20.284 --> 00:35:22.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I will do everything</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in my power to save it.</c.bg_transparent>

607
00:35:22.870 --> 00:35:25.623 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, are you going to</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>tell these people to go</c.bg_transparent>

608
00:35:25.706 --> 00:35:26.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>or shall I?</c.bg_transparent>

609
00:35:32.421 --> 00:35:33.714 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My children</c.bg_transparent>

610
00:35:33.798 --> 00:35:35.758 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>the Prophets have heard your prayers.</c.bg_transparent>

611
00:35:35.842 --> 00:35:37.176 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You must go.</c.bg_transparent>

612
00:35:41.556 --> 00:35:43.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Take them to the transports.</c.bg_transparent>

613
00:35:45.768 --> 00:35:47.311 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All right, this way.</c.bg_transparent>

614
00:35:47.436 --> 00:35:49.772 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Congratulations, Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

615
00:35:49.856 --> 00:35:52.567 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thanks to you the Prophets'</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>victory is at hand.</c.bg_transparent>

616
00:35:52.650 --> 00:35:54.026 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hope you're right.</c.bg_transparent>

617
00:35:54.652 --> 00:35:56.571 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where is your faith, Emissary?</c.bg_transparent>

618
00:35:56.946 --> 00:35:59.907 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't think the Evil One</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>will be victorious, do you?</c.bg_transparent>

619
00:36:01.284 --> 00:36:04.871 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Rest assured, the Golden Age is upon us.</c.bg_transparent>

620
00:36:05.580 --> 00:36:08.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets and the people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>will be as one.</c.bg_transparent>

621
00:36:09.542 --> 00:36:10.626 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Think of it.</c.bg_transparent>

622
00:36:10.710 --> 00:36:14.005 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There will be no need for vedeks or kais</c.bg_transparent>

623
00:36:14.589 --> 00:36:16.340 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>or even Emissaries.</c.bg_transparent>

624
00:36:19.719 --> 00:36:22.263 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kosst Amojan has chosen its vessel.</c.bg_transparent>

625
00:36:34.525 --> 00:36:35.902 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let it begin.</c.bg_transparent>

626
00:36:44.535 --> 00:36:46.996 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Leave my son and take me instead!</c.bg_transparent>

627
00:36:48.998 --> 00:36:51.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your Emissary offers himself to us.</c.bg_transparent>

628
00:36:52.627 --> 00:36:53.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>His faith wavers.</c.bg_transparent>

629
00:36:55.546 --> 00:36:56.839 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunting )</c.bg_transparent>

630
00:37:07.391 --> 00:37:08.976 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groaning )</c.bg_transparent>

631
00:37:34.794 --> 00:37:36.712 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Emissary, we must go.</c.bg_transparent>

632
00:37:48.224 --> 00:37:50.184 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Benjamin, Worf is standing by in Ops.</c.bg_transparent>

633
00:37:50.268 --> 00:37:53.062 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He can trigger the chroniton generator</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at your command.</c.bg_transparent>

634
00:37:53.145 --> 00:37:54.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can still end this, Ben.</c.bg_transparent>

635
00:37:54.355 --> 00:37:55.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, I've got to play this thing out.</c.bg_transparent>

636
00:37:55.940 --> 00:37:57.525 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That is your son out there.</c.bg_transparent>

637
00:37:57.608 --> 00:38:00.403 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you think I know that?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets will protect him.</c.bg_transparent>

638
00:38:00.736 --> 00:38:02.113 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're trying to kill him.</c.bg_transparent>

639
00:38:02.196 --> 00:38:04.782 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No. They're trying</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to destroy the Pah-wraith.</c.bg_transparent>

640
00:38:04.865 --> 00:38:07.368 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets will not let</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>anything happen to him.</c.bg_transparent>

641
00:38:07.493 --> 00:38:08.703 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How do you know that?</c.bg_transparent>

642
00:38:08.786 --> 00:38:09.912 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know.</c.bg_transparent>

643
00:38:12.164 --> 00:38:13.332 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've got to get out of here.</c.bg_transparent>

644
00:38:13.416 --> 00:38:14.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>According to the sensors,</c.bg_transparent>

645
00:38:14.834 --> 00:38:18.045 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>the energy building between them</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>could explode at any second.</c.bg_transparent>

646
00:38:18.129 --> 00:38:19.755 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not going to leave Jake here.</c.bg_transparent>

647
00:38:21.674 --> 00:38:23.467 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We must go, Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

648
00:38:23.551 --> 00:38:24.552 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Benjamin...</c.bg_transparent>

649
00:38:24.635 --> 00:38:27.346 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get out of here!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Get off the station, both of you!</c.bg_transparent>

650
00:38:27.430 --> 00:38:28.472 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's an order!</c.bg_transparent>

651
00:38:28.556 --> 00:38:29.849 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come, child. We must go.</c.bg_transparent>

652
00:38:38.816 --> 00:38:39.817 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dax to Worf.</c.bg_transparent>

653
00:38:43.612 --> 00:38:44.655 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

654
00:38:44.739 --> 00:38:46.907 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Meet me at Airlock Eight. We're leaving.</c.bg_transparent>

655
00:38:50.953 --> 00:38:53.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go on ahead.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Airlock Eight is down to the right.</c.bg_transparent>

656
00:38:54.248 --> 00:38:56.667 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This way. Move quickly.</c.bg_transparent>

657
00:38:56.751 --> 00:38:58.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's go. Come on.</c.bg_transparent>

658
00:38:58.878 --> 00:38:59.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hurry up.</c.bg_transparent>

659
00:39:00.046 --> 00:39:02.089 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's okay, it's okay.</c.bg_transparent>

660
00:39:02.298 --> 00:39:03.716 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think the transport is down here.</c.bg_transparent>

661
00:39:29.158 --> 00:39:31.118 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No!</c.bg_transparent>

662
00:39:32.119 --> 00:39:35.122 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>COMPUTER:</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Chroniton levels at 37% and rising.</i></c.bg_transparent>

663
00:39:37.208 --> 00:39:39.335 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>May the Prophets forgive me.</c.bg_transparent>

664
00:40:03.317 --> 00:40:04.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Jake...</c.bg_transparent>

665
00:40:13.285 --> 00:40:15.329 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Captain's Log, supplemental.</i></c.bg_transparent>

666
00:40:15.538 --> 00:40:19.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>The station's population</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>has returned</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>and repairs are underway.</i></c.bg_transparent>

667
00:40:19.834 --> 00:40:22.753 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Major Kira has recovered</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>from her experience...</i></c.bg_transparent>

668
00:40:22.837 --> 00:40:25.798 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>but my son is still</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>in the Infirmary.</i></c.bg_transparent>

669
00:40:27.216 --> 00:40:28.217 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Jake?</c.bg_transparent>

670
00:40:28.300 --> 00:40:31.178 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He'll be, uh, laid up for a few days</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but he'll be all right.</c.bg_transparent>

671
00:40:31.387 --> 00:40:32.346 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>May I see him?</c.bg_transparent>

672
00:40:32.430 --> 00:40:33.347 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, yes.</c.bg_transparent>

673
00:40:41.355 --> 00:40:42.314 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Jake...</c.bg_transparent>

674
00:40:45.776 --> 00:40:46.861 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dad.</c.bg_transparent>

675
00:40:47.403 --> 00:40:48.487 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How are you feeling?</c.bg_transparent>

676
00:40:49.780 --> 00:40:51.323 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Could be worse.</c.bg_transparent>

677
00:40:53.242 --> 00:40:55.119 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll be up and about in no time.</c.bg_transparent>

678
00:40:58.414 --> 00:41:00.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know what to say.</c.bg_transparent>

679
00:41:01.792 --> 00:41:03.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Say you're happy to see me.</c.bg_transparent>

680
00:41:04.795 --> 00:41:06.172 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know I am.</c.bg_transparent>

681
00:41:08.674 --> 00:41:10.092 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish I...</c.bg_transparent>

682
00:41:12.553 --> 00:41:14.513 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want to explain what happened...</c.bg_transparent>

683
00:41:16.765 --> 00:41:18.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I'm not sure that I can.</c.bg_transparent>

684
00:41:20.728 --> 00:41:22.313 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't have to explain.</c.bg_transparent>

685
00:41:23.731 --> 00:41:25.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>When the Pah-wraith was inside me</c.bg_transparent>

686
00:41:27.067 --> 00:41:28.777 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I could feel its hatred</c.bg_transparent>

687
00:41:29.778 --> 00:41:33.199 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I knew that no matter what</c.bg_transparent>

688
00:41:33.824 --> 00:41:35.784 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>it couldn't be allowed to win...</c.bg_transparent>

689
00:41:38.120 --> 00:41:39.997 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>even if it meant I had to die.</c.bg_transparent>

690
00:41:43.083 --> 00:41:44.502 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You did the right thing.</c.bg_transparent>

691
00:41:58.516 --> 00:42:00.142 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How was the prayer service?</c.bg_transparent>

692
00:42:00.226 --> 00:42:02.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>To tell you the truth</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't pay that much attention.</c.bg_transparent>

693
00:42:02.853 --> 00:42:05.356 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm still trying to make sense</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>out of everything that happened.</c.bg_transparent>

694
00:42:05.439 --> 00:42:09.652 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I mean, of all the people on this station</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Prophets chose me.</c.bg_transparent>

695
00:42:10.027 --> 00:42:13.948 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not sure I know why</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I deserve that honor.</c.bg_transparent>

696
00:42:14.031 --> 00:42:16.700 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps that's why you were chosen.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You have faith and humility.</c.bg_transparent>

697
00:42:16.784 --> 00:42:18.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I heard that you told the Captain</c.bg_transparent>

698
00:42:19.078 --> 00:42:21.539 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that I was willing to give my life</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to serve the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

699
00:42:22.790 --> 00:42:25.209 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I appreciate that you respect my beliefs.</c.bg_transparent>

700
00:42:26.377 --> 00:42:30.965 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just the same, I wouldn't have minded</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if the Prophets had chosen someone else.</c.bg_transparent>

701
00:42:33.717 --> 00:42:35.094 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have to go.</c.bg_transparent>

702
00:42:35.177 --> 00:42:38.389 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll drop by Security</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>after I take the Kai to her shuttle.</c.bg_transparent>

703
00:42:48.107 --> 00:42:50.734 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Emissary couldn't escort me himself?</c.bg_transparent>

704
00:42:51.277 --> 00:42:52.611 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's with his son.</c.bg_transparent>

705
00:42:52.820 --> 00:42:54.989 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I would think he'd want to thank me.</c.bg_transparent>

706
00:42:55.072 --> 00:42:56.615 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For what?</c.bg_transparent>

707
00:42:56.949 --> 00:42:59.952 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I prevented the destruction</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of this station.</c.bg_transparent>

708
00:43:00.035 --> 00:43:04.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I saved the Emissary's life</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and the life of his son.</c.bg_transparent>

709
00:43:04.206 --> 00:43:06.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't pretend you did it for the Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

710
00:43:07.251 --> 00:43:08.919 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I did it for Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

711
00:43:09.169 --> 00:43:12.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you haven't heard,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the floodwaters have receded</c.bg_transparent>

712
00:43:12.506 --> 00:43:14.216 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and the earthquakes have stopped.</c.bg_transparent>

713
00:43:14.300 --> 00:43:16.302 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you're going to take credit for that?</c.bg_transparent>

714
00:43:17.761 --> 00:43:20.472 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I take it as a sign I did the right thing.</c.bg_transparent>

715
00:43:20.556 --> 00:43:22.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You defied the will of the Prophets</c.bg_transparent>

716
00:43:22.600 --> 00:43:23.892 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and you did it</c.bg_transparent>

717
00:43:23.976 --> 00:43:27.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>because you couldn't stand</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the fact that a human, an infidel,</c.bg_transparent>

718
00:43:28.689 --> 00:43:30.566 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>had a stronger faith than you.</c.bg_transparent>

719
00:43:31.066 --> 00:43:33.611 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Emissary was willing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to sacrifice his own son</c.bg_transparent>

720
00:43:33.694 --> 00:43:35.154 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to serve the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

721
00:43:35.863 --> 00:43:38.699 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My faith is as pure as the Emissary's.</c.bg_transparent>

722
00:43:40.075 --> 00:43:43.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think you're confusing faith</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with ambition.</c.bg_transparent>

723
00:43:43.954 --> 00:43:47.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not confusing anything,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>child, you are.</c.bg_transparent>

724
00:43:48.167 --> 00:43:51.295 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets chose you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as their instrument.</c.bg_transparent>

725
00:43:51.378 --> 00:43:54.298 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That doesn't mean you can speak for them.</c.bg_transparent>

726
00:43:54.757 --> 00:43:58.177 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Because of your interference,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Reckoning was stopped.</c.bg_transparent>

727
00:43:58.260 --> 00:44:00.179 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The evil still exists.</c.bg_transparent>

728
00:44:01.096 --> 00:44:05.142 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And I'm not sure if even the Prophets know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what that will mean for Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

